What more can you ask for then a road trip with the bros?! How bout a van that isn't yours to a apartment that you get to stay at in the city with spots littered around it! We loaded up the mini-van and made the trek to San Fran from O'side with a tight krue who was ready to laugh all the way there and rip the spots ta boot. SF is the real streets and if you can get it done there, you shouldn't have a problem too many other places.

Featuring: Cruise Mosberg, Victor Aceves, & Bobby Long.

Video by: Jacob Nunez
Additional filming: Andres Bill Garcia

node.text:
When you live down unda' and have to come to Oceanside to hang out with the bros a lot, a fanny pack or a backpack won't do. @jacksonpilz needed a bigger bag, so we made him one. 
A simple run of the mill skateboard edit just would suffice either, so we challenged ourselves to get Xtreme! Jackson accepted said challenge and conquered.

The Bumbag Co Jackson Pilz duffle bag, made of tan canvas and brown nubuck suede, has compartments lined with forest green because Jackson’s favorite Rhoades brother is Forrest.

Tap that link in bio to shop!

video by @justsomedude
